name: Liminal Strawberry Jam
description:
Initially recovered from a storage locker in Jita, which had been seized due to unpaid fees, and its contents put up for auction. 

The storage locker came with a shipping docket listing its contents and their origin as the system of Niarja, not long after its occupation by the Triglavians. 

Rather oddly, it seems that many of the jars are empty, and those that do still have a filling seem to be remarkably well preserved and have a warm reddish glow to them.

It’s labelled as all-natural and safe to eat… probably.
